text:
You've been working hard all this time.
Good job, Juri.

Yeah, and you too, Producer.
We made it through to the end because of you.

Huh?
No, I didn't do anything...

You made sure to put on the brakes, right?
Without that, we might have overdone it.

But that's my role,
to watch over you and everyone else.

...!
This drink... isn't it yours, Juri?

Both of us did a great job!
To the wrap-up party!

Haha, after going home,
I feel like I can work even harder...!

Hey hey... For now,
let's forget about work and enjoy ourselves, okay?
